room_title: Escape room "Battleship" by Red Door Escapes in Little Rock
room_description: In Red Door Escapes’ premier adventure, set sail aboard the USS Enigma, a secret naval warship prowling the Pacific ocean during the height of the Cold War. The Captain is missing, the XO is in charge, the crew is growing restless, and the ship is headed for disaster only YOU can change the course of the USS Enigma, and maybe…just maybe…the course of history!
